Has it nothing to do with you?

246
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:47,940
At any rate, I have lost my memory, haven't I?

247
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:50,760
This argument is so peculiar.

248
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:53,900
I don't know whether Xiao Bai will think the same way or not.

249
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:07,190
Then... I am really going.

250
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:09,850
You will be back.

251
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:15,270
You big obstacle, where does your confidence come from?

252
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:26,140
Brother are right! Everything Brother says is right.

253
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:28,240
This is my home, isn't it?

254
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:32,710
You should wait for me here. I'll certainly come back to see Older Brother.

255
00:19:53,820 --> 00:19:57,650
[Hua Residence]

256
00:20:04,170 --> 00:20:06,900
Little Chun Hua already left.

257
00:20:06,900 --> 00:20:10,930
What method should I use to make her come back obediently of her own accord?

258
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:14,350
I have an idea you can try.

259
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,630
Say it.

260
00:20:16,630 --> 00:20:21,570
If Xiao Bai comes back, then so will Miss Chun Hua.

261
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:25,190
Interesting, keep talking!

262
00:20:25,690 --> 00:20:30,060
Everyone knows the thing Young Master Xiao cares about the most

263
00:20:30,060 --> 00:20:32,130
is the longevity fruit.

264
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:36,500
Now that you mention it, I didn't hear any news of the longevity fruit in a while.

265
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:39,400
I understand. I will get to work.

266
00:20:42,170 --> 00:20:44,590
Longevity fruit?

267
00:20:52,040 --> 00:20:55,410
Sisi, recently, it's rumored that

268
00:20:55,410 --> 00:20:59,480
the longevity fruit flows out of the healer's hands,

269
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,710
and it can bring the dead back to life.

270
00:21:01,710 --> 00:21:04,690
Where on earth could there be such a wonderful thing?

271
00:21:04,690 --> 00:21:09,160
Husband, I don't believe in it.

272
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:11,420
As long as I'm able to cure your illness,

273
00:21:11,420 --> 00:21:13,630
even if there's just a sliver of hope,

274
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:15,560
I still believe in it.

275
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:22,410
What is this?

276
00:21:26,870 --> 00:21:28,680
Take a look, Wife.

277
00:21:32,950 --> 00:21:36,180
[A prize for guessing correctly]

278
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:39,610
It's a lantern riddle.

279
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:45,180
The red string is a lantern riddle. The string!

280
00:21:45,730 --> 00:21:48,610
It is related to me.

281
00:21:48,610 --> 00:21:51,010
Let me think about it.

282
00:21:52,210 --> 00:21:55,020
A colored string...

283
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:59,760
means the character for "cut off."

284
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:01,780
Cut...

285
00:22:02,330 --> 00:22:04,500
A dead end?

286
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:07,240
A hopeless situation?

287
00:22:09,690 --> 00:22:11,520
My husband,

288
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:16,960
why does it sound a bit unlucky?

289
00:22:22,950 --> 00:22:26,200
Sisi, you always love to think too much.

290
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,130
It's actually a compliment.

291
00:22:28,130 --> 00:22:30,090
It means "a remarkably beautiful woman."

292
00:22:38,330 --> 00:22:41,440
Master, I have news about Mr. Shi.

293
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:49,110
Brother Xiao, have you really decided to return like this?

294
00:22:49,690 --> 00:22:51,540
The Hua family unexpectedly called off the engagement.

295
00:22:51,540 --> 00:22:54,100
I did not foresee this.

296
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:58,350
I plan to make a decision after discussing it with my father.

297
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:05,220
- Too bad! Marriage arrangement has separated so many lovers. 
 - I heard the longevity fruit surfaced again.

298
00:23:06,630 --> 00:23:08,710
Quick, go and take a look.

299
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:10,740
The longevity fruit?

300
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,530
Chief.

301
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:27,040
Chief Leng.

302
00:23:31,320 --> 00:23:34,290
Chief Leng is on our side, so there's no need to be secretive.

303
00:23:34,290 --> 00:23:38,800
According to my scouts, clues to the longevity fruit have resurfaced.

304
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:41,890
Where is it?

305
00:23:41,890 --> 00:23:45,060
Yetan City, with the Hua family.

306
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:57,140
[Official Notice: Longevity fruit calmly waits for the man who is destined. If interested, see the Hua family.]

307
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,630
- The Hua family? 
 - Who is the destined man?

308
00:24:01,630 --> 00:24:05,610
Yes! "The destined man..." What's going on?

309
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:08,420
To the Hua! Excuse me.

310
00:24:08,420 --> 00:24:12,790
I wondered why Xiao Bai suddenly planned to go to Yetan City to see the festival lanterns.

311
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:15,970
Now I see that he made these plans ahead of time.

312
00:24:15,970 --> 00:24:19,130
He wants to grab the longevity fruit first before others.

313
00:24:19,130 --> 00:24:21,120
Since you trust me,

314
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:24,370
then I will act according to your plan.

315
00:24:34,170 --> 00:24:36,480
The guest you're talking about has already left.

316
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,590
Left? When did he leave?

317
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,990
He's been gone for a while now.

318
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:43,430
I don't know any martial arts.

319
00:24:43,430 --> 00:24:44,980
If I want to chase after Xiao Bai,

320
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:47,970
I'll never catch up with him.

321
00:24:57,050 --> 00:24:58,850
Don't worry! It'll be done soon.

322
00:24:58,850 --> 00:25:00,440
Now, be careful!

323
00:25:02,420 --> 00:25:07,810
- Eat while it's hot. 
 - Buns! Hot steamed buns!

324
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:11,310
Sir, I'll have two orders of steamed buns.

325
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:17,370
Miss Caicai?

326
00:25:18,050 --> 00:25:20,210
Miss Chun Hua?

327
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:33,360
Miss Chun Hua, what are you doing here?

328
00:25:34,890 --> 00:25:37,660
I still want to elope with you.

329
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:43,400
Steamed meat buns!

330
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:49,040
Why did you all leave so quickly?

331
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:52,930
Just now when I returned to the inn, the young innkeeper said you all left.

332
00:25:52,930 --> 00:25:54,970
But why have you returned?

333
00:25:54,970 --> 00:25:58,120
There's an important matter so I must return to the Hua family.

334
00:26:04,650 --> 00:26:08,220
I... I finally got away from the Hua family after so much trouble. What?

335
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:10,220
And now are you saying you want to return?

336
00:26:10,220 --> 00:26:12,110
Xiao Bai, let me tell you this,

337
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:15,510
our marriage doesn't need my brother's and father's approvals. Truly!

338
00:26:15,510 --> 00:26:18,260
- If we return to Fengming Mountain Manor, we can... 
 - It's not about that.

339
00:26:18,260 --> 00:26:21,370
Listen! You truly don't need to be afraid of my brother or father.

340
00:26:21,370 --> 00:26:24,040
- I'm being serious. You just need to... 
 - Miss Chun Hua.

341
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:27,210
Right now, the longevity fruit appeared at the Hua residence.

342
00:26:27,210 --> 00:26:29,670
The chief of the martial arts circles has been waiting for it to save his life.

343
00:26:29,670 --> 00:26:33,130
Therefore, this matter is of the greatest urgency.

344
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:37,960
So he's not returning for my sake.

345
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:40,370
This time, I think only we three should go.

346
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:44,060
Miss Feng and Miss Leng, just return to the inn and wait for my news.

347
00:26:50,460 --> 00:26:52,460
[Hua Residence]

348
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:41,790
My Sister! My Sweet Sister, where have you been?

349
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:44,070
Father and I were so worried about you.

350
00:27:44,070 --> 00:27:46,740
It's fine! What matters is you've returned home. Let's go!

351
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:48,640
Brother Hua.

352
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,850
When did you two get here?

353
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:57,640
Thank you, Hero Xiao, for personally escorting Xiaolei home.

354
00:27:57,640 --> 00:28:00,240
But there's nothing for you here, you should leave now.

355
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:02,400
Wait a moment, Brother Hua!

356
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:07,280
Haven't we said that Xiaolei is not marrying you?

357
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:10,410
Hero Xiao, how can you have no sense of shame?

358
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:11,900
Brother Hua, you're crossing the line.

359
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:15,810
Regardless if Xiaolei marries him or not, the Xiao and Hua families all are old friends.

360
00:28:15,810 --> 00:28:19,000
- Brother Hua, you should not lose your sense of propriety. 
 - And who might you be?

361
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,900
So what if I lost my sense of propriety?

362
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:23,290
Brother Hua, please listen to my brief remarks.

363
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:27,390
The reason I'm here is absolutely not due to the engagement matter, but for a much more critical issue.

364
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:29,410
May I have a word with you in private?

365
00:28:29,410 --> 00:28:31,840
Why can't you say it here?

366
00:28:33,620 --> 00:28:36,860
I'm afraid that this place is not quite suitable.

367
00:28:36,860 --> 00:28:39,340
Hero Xiao, if you're unable to speak clearly,

368
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:41,180
then forgive me for being unable to accompany you.

369
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:45,380
- Butler! Send them away. 
 - Brother Hua, to be honest,

370
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:48,840
I want to ask you about the matter of the longevity fruit.

371
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:58,120
Well, regarding that, it's really not appropriate to speak here.

372
00:28:58,120 --> 00:29:00,120
Please come in!

373
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:01,850
Thank you.

374
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:11,220
I said you will hate to part with me but I didn't expect you to return so quickly.

375
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:14,720
When Xiao Bai finishes tending to his affairs, he'll take me away with him. You'll see!

376
00:29:17,010 --> 00:29:19,160
I hope so.

377
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:23,620
You all may take your time but I'm taking my leave now.

378
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:35,810
Hero Xiao, could it be that you'd like to question us separately?

379
00:29:35,810 --> 00:29:38,330
Brother Hua, why would you say such a thing?

380
00:29:39,590 --> 00:29:43,000
The one whom my sister fell in love with is indeed smart.

381
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:46,130
If I'm guessing correctly, just now, that young master

382
00:29:46,130 --> 00:29:48,280
is going to looking for my father.

383
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:50,440
Am I right?

384
00:29:52,210 --> 00:29:55,430
Xiao Bai is definitely not the complicated man that you say he is.

385
00:29:56,690 --> 00:29:59,040
Brother Hua, since you get straight to the point,

386
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:01,190
there's no need for me to hold back.

387
00:30:01,190 --> 00:30:05,890
Brother Hua, I hope you can understand how I need the longevity fruit to save my father.

388
00:30:06,570 --> 00:30:09,220
Of course, I understand your difficulties, Hero Xiao.

389
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:11,900
Otherwise, I wouldn't have let you all in.

390
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:15,780
Come to speak of it,

391
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:19,180
does Brother Hua know the location of the longevity fruit?

392
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:22,270
This...

393
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:27,910
Sister,

394
00:30:28,650 --> 00:30:31,690
do you think we should tell Hero Xiao

395
00:30:31,690 --> 00:30:33,930
our Hua family secret?

396
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:43,680
Does our family have a secret?

397
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:47,970
You're joking around again! Have you forgotten what happened yesterday?

398
00:30:47,970 --> 00:30:51,440
Y-Yesterday?

399
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:54,280
Yesterday... y-yesterday?

400
00:30:54,280 --> 00:30:57,260
Xiao Bai, what is he talking about? I truly have no idea.

401
00:31:01,190 --> 00:31:03,240
Since you don't want to talk about it,

402
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:07,840
then I must become an unfilial son.

403
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:11,910
To tell you the truth, the longevity fruit is at our manor,

404
00:31:11,910 --> 00:31:14,840
