407
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:23,250
He said he wanted to write an official notice.

408
00:31:24,690 --> 00:31:27,320
So Master Hua wrote the notice?

409
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:30,360
I never wrote any kind of notice.

410
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:33,800
Moreover, I don't even know what the longevity fruit is.

411
00:31:33,800 --> 00:31:37,520
Someone must be purposely framing me.

412
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:40,860
Uncle Hua, if you don't feel at ease,

413
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:43,830
I can give you my guarantee.

414
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:47,060
If you have any terms or conditions, please do not hesitate to tell me.

415
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:49,330
This is truly preposterous!

416
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:54,130
I have urged my father before,

417
00:31:54,130 --> 00:31:56,570
