419
00:31:58,610 --> 00:32:01,400
It would be a great contribution to the martial arts circles.

420
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:05,520
Moreover, our families are longtime friends.

421
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:11,230
However, he didn't think so.

422
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:14,120
Contrary to expectations, Father simply did not understand this logic.

423
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:16,840
He still insisted on announcing this to the whole world.

424
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:19,300
He said he wants to sell it for a good price.

425
00:32:19,850 --> 00:32:24,470
Oh, that's right! Hero Xiao, speaking of my sister's wedding,

426
00:32:24,470 --> 00:32:28,550
Actually, I've been in awe and admiring you this entire time.

427
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:31,490
It's just that my father fears affection will grow in Sister's heart,

428
00:32:31,490 --> 00:32:33,720
