429
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:36,440
Therefore, we decided to break off the engagement.

430
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:50,030
No, no, no! Not that.

431
00:32:50,030 --> 00:32:53,460
I truly did not know anything about this matter. Truly!

